      <abstract>
        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides guidance to prospective DHCPv6 option developers to help them create option formats that are easily adoptable by existing DHCPv6 software.  It also provides guidelines for expert reviewers to evaluate new registrations.  This document updates RFC 3315.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
